                            <comment id="306420" author="adilger" created="Wed, 7 Jul 2021 07:14:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is still failing about 10% of all runs, starting on 2021-03-01.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Between 2021-01-01 and 2021-02-28, it only failed 4 times, once per week in January for &lt;tt&gt;full-patchless&lt;/tt&gt; test sessions, and not in February at all.  From 2021-03-01 to about 2021-05-29 it is failing about 8 times per week for patch review test runs, and since 2021-05-29 it is failing about 5 times per day.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="305497" author="adilger" created="Fri, 25 Jun 2021 07:04:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is is failing 10% of all test runs, 67 times in the past 4 weeks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
